00:25:52.610 --> 00:25:53.650
Todos me esperas aquí.

00:25:53.650 --> 00:25:54.810
Iré a echar un vistazo.

00:25:55.410 --> 00:25:56.730
Mantente a salvo, Liuxi.

00:26:21.450 --> 00:26:22.370
Gao Shen,

00:26:28.050 --> 00:26:29.130
