00:26:29.890 --> 00:26:31.050
Yo soy, Ye Liuxi.

00:26:31.970 --> 00:26:33.090
Ahora es seguro.

00:26:33.090 --> 00:26:34.210
Puedes salir.

00:26:36.770 --> 00:26:37.570
Gao Shen.

00:26:38.810 --> 00:26:40.210
